description: REMARKABLE SOUTHIE CONDO!!! Spacious open floor plan condo, in an Unbeatable Location! This freshly painted, first-floor two-bedroom condo features stunning hardwood floors throughout leading to a relaxing living area.  The modern open layout kitchen offers granite counters and updated Stainless Steel appliance package with gas cooking.  Other features include washer/dryer in unit, bathtub, convenient hallway linen closet, ample closets in both bedrooms, and a basement storage unit, providing ample space to store all your belongings. What truly sets this home apart is its phenomenal location in South Boston.  You'll be at the epicenter of vibrant living, with West Broadway's renowned restaurants and nightlife just steps away.  Plus, easy access to I-93, I-90, and multiple bus routes ensure you can explore the city effortlessly.  And, if you love the beach, you're just a quick 5-minute drive from M St Beach! Schedule a showing and make this your new home sweet home!
